---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Advertising Disclosure • Fin Sanctuary"
  description="Read the Fin Sanctuary advertising disclosure covering AdSense placements and how advertising supports the site."
>
  <main>
    <section class="border-b border-primary/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(1,133,174,0.08),rgba(243,239,238,0.55))] dark:border-white/8 dark:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(13,175,188,0.14),rgba(2,6,23,0.95))]">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10 md:py-12">
        <div class="text-[0.72rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary/75">Advertising Disclosure</div>
        <h1 class="mt-5 font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">How advertising appears on Fin Sanctuary.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          Fin Sanctuary may display advertising, including Google AdSense placements, to support the cost of building and publishing free aquarium content.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10">
      <article class="rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/10 bg-white px-7 py-8 shadow-[0_24px_80px_-55px_rgba(1,133,174,0.42)] dark:border-white/8 dark:bg-slate-900 md:px-9">
        <div class="space-y-7 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Advertising May Appear</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">Pages on Fin Sanctuary may display ad units, including Google AdSense placements, in order to help fund guide creation, media publishing, and site maintenance.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Ads Are Not Endorsements</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">An advertisement appearing on the site does not automatically mean Fin Sanctuary recommends, endorses, or has personally reviewed the advertiser or the advertised product.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Editorial Separation</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">The goal is to keep educational content useful on its own, with advertising layered in cleanly rather than used as a substitute for real guidance. Content should stay planning-first and care-first.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Advertising Providers</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">Third-party ad providers may use their own systems, cookies, and measurement tools. Readers should review the relevant provider policies for more detail about how those systems work.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
